strings.Value: "You know, the author of my favorite books was a follower of the Dawnflower. His name was Ash. He wasn't a man of the cloth like you Tristian; he dabbled in the arcane arts. But he did find Sarenrae's teaching an ideology to live by."
"I like the sound of this Ash. Perhaps I will have to give those books a read. Legend of the Archknights of Avistan was it?"
